    "body": "### Problem\n\nWhen installing Neovim 0.12 (Neovim.Neovim.Nightly) via winget, an error message appears: “Installer hash does not match.”\n\n### Steps to reproduce\n\nwinget install Neovim.Neovim.Nightly\n\n### Expected behavior\n\nInstall version 0.12 correctly\n\n### Nvim version (nvim -v)\n\n0.12.0 commit fc7e5cf\n\n### Vim (not Nvim) behaves the same?\n\nno\n\n### Operating system/version\n\nwindows 11 (25H2)\n\n### Terminal name/version\n\nWindows Terminal Preview\n\n### $TERM environment variable\n\nnush\n\n### Installation\n\nwinget",
